Stem:
The capital structure of Super Power Co. Ltd. is given below:

13% Common Stock: 3,50,000 Taka;

12% Preferred Stock: 2,00,000 Taka;

10% Debenture: 3,00,000 Taka.

Total = 8,50,000 Taka.

Next year, the company's expected rate of return on profit is 20%.

The capital structure of Sony Company Limited is as follows:

Common Stock: 10,00,000 Taka;

10% Preferred Stock: 2,50,000 Taka;

14% Debenture: 7,50,000 Taka.

Total = 20,00,000 Taka.

The selling price of each common share is 50 Taka. The expected rate of return (dividend) this year is 4 Taka. The dividend growth rate is 5%. The company's tax rate is 40%.
